financial markets true partner capital strives to generate uncorrelated returns for its clients and investors with an emphasis on outperformance in times of market turmoil as such we strongly believe volatility should be treated as a separate asset class allowing for improved riskreward characteristics of investment portfolios team and technology true partner capital is a team of former market makers and it specialists that have been working together for more than  years their combined expertise on trading execution and risk management as well as the proprietary trading technology allows the team to identify and capitalize on trading opportunities funds and managed accounts the true partner fund inception july  applies an active global volatility arbitrage investment strategy aiming to generate uncorrelated returns by using a volatility neutral approach the true partner volatility master fund inception september 6 utilizes a similar methodology to identify underpriced and overpriced volatility but applies an overall long volatility bias as a result this fund would be expected to generate more negatively correlated returns besides these funds true partner capital can also provide specifically engineered solutions for investors looking to optimize the riskreward profile of their overall portfolio for further information please send your request through the contact page fund news contact true partner fund true partner news true partner panel member at fow’s derivative world asia conference true partner capital usa joins the global volatility summit in new york again on march  true partner revisits the context summit miami in february  true partner article  and now for something completely different cboe rmc asia feel the burn  long volatility exposures for hedging and alpha true partner on bloomberg tv postbrexit optimism ebbs govert heijboer of the true partner fund about the volatility strategy and performance  by ralph van put global asset management true partner tr