fund has secured a  return making it one of the strongerperforming volarb funds in the asian space despite the challenging environment its longshort volatility strategy with a marketneutral approach has already grown to  million in size and is looking to scale capacity to  million heijboer and his team at true partner had worked at market maker saen options in the netherlands but he moved to hong kong in  with the rest of the crew bringing a crossregional flavour to the operation while the fund takes a longshort view on index volatility across the globe including that of sp  its trades are mostly set in asia where heijboer thinks that most mispricing and inefficiencies originate “within the region itself we can hedge korea against japan or against hong kong and we also deliver regional hedges between asia and the us or europe” says heijboer the fund on average runs  shortterm positions – mostly index volatility followed by single stocks and then a small portion on interest rates    this coverarticle can be downloaded as a pdf and is available at the website of hedgefund intelligence download the pdf go to the website of hedgefund intelligence asiahedge published by ralph van put   true partner volatility us fund lp  pooled investment fund heijboer formdscom  sec filings of fundraisings and investments in hedge funds private equity firms startups and growing companies formdscom newest filter local true partner volatility us fund lp industry pooled investment fund see others in industry address co true partner volatility gp llc  west jackson blvd suite  chicago il phone  6 filings date filingtype reported sold incremental cash type exemptions link to raw filing 6 new   other b c c sec link 6 new yet to sell  other b c c sec link directors and executives current and past name role godefriedus govert heijboer executive tobias hekster director na true partner advisor hong kong limited executive na true partner advisor limited executive na true partner capital usa holding